README

AngularRestPy: a boiler plate for Flask backend and Angular front end based apps, restful APIs

Build Backend:

In the Backend folder, create a virtual environment:

virtualenv --no-site-packages venv

activate it:

. venv/bin/activate

Install the backend:

python setup.py install

Create the database:

paster --plugin=server create_db config.ini createall

Run backend server:

paster serve config.ini

Access the Backend APIs at:

http://127.0.0.1:5000/server/api/worker


Build Frontend

Install node packages:

npm install

Initiate Karma for unit testing:

node_modules/karma/bin/karma init